    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the defined COU. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all 5 evaluated operating points.",
